item.title: Tic-tac-toe game for time
item.description: Unlike other tic-tac-toe games, this computer plays really hard and even harshly. In addition, the time to think about a move is limited to a few seconds. So you have to think very quickly. On the other hand, such an approach will only further develop your brains, ingenuity and cunning. Mouse control.
